            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-coffee-dark mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">
                        What Do We Cover?
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-coffee-brown leading-relaxed opacity-90">
                        Our coffee blog covers various topics within the industry, including coffee culture, coffee and your health, coffee drink comparisons, and much more. Be it the newest coffee trend, the history of coffee, or the science of caffeine—we have it all.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="border-t md:border-t-0 md:border-l border-coffee-brown/10 pt-8 md:pt-0 md:pl-10">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-coffee-dark mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">
                        Why visit our blog?
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-coffee-brown leading-relaxed italic opacity-80 text-sm">
                        Imagine you’re on holiday with no espresso machine. You need your morning cup of Joe, but no coffee shop surrounds you. What do you do? You visit Zaidly. We help you find answers on making coffee with minimal gear, mastering new techniques, or simply enjoying stories about the craft when you can't have a cup yourself.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
